{"tid":1139494,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下大家我應該點做","createTime":"2019-05-05T09:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T10:09:12.000Z","uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"60157917befc53f7cc9d7c0993cb90f7ce9c8ee0","tid":1139494,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:56:15.000Z","msg":"我同我前度拍左幾年拖<br />\n我同我前度2017年底和平分左手<br />\n上年年頭佢懷疑自己有cancer <br />\n喊哂口咁搵我陪佢睇醫生<br />\n雖然最後唔係絕症<br />\n不過都確診係內分泌既病<br />\n病因係壓力而導致<br />\n最少要食藥一年睇下情況受唔受控而決定好唔好得返<br />\n其實我都好關心佢 不過我知唔係愛情果種<br />\n所以慢慢見佢病情受控我都鄧佢開心<br />\n大約上年冬天我同佢慢慢無乜聯絡<br />\n因為節日氣氛驅使<br />\n所以我down 左交友app 識左一個女仔<br />\n我同佢一拍即合<br />\n雖然我本身無打算咁快拍拖<br />\n但好快我發現我真係鐘意左佢<br />\n所以4月我地正式一齊左<br />\n有一次我同呢個女仔出街<br />\n用電話佢睇緊連登post <br />\n我前度無啦啦WhatsApp 問我1d普通野<br />\n其實自從上年冬天佢好耐無whatsapp 我<br />\n重點係我發現我未轉佢個名<br />\n仲係以前拍拖既whatsapp名（係咪水洗都洗唔清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n個女仔見到 於是佢唔開心同唔信我<br />\n同埋之前有一次<br />\n係IG 個女仔係我d 相到留左d比較親暱既野<br />\n我果陣下意識archive 左張相（非合照）<br />\n我諗我當時係唔想我前度見到住啦<br />\n我後尾有當面同我前度講左我識左新女朋友<br />\n但總之呢兩件事 <br />\n個女仔而家對我係完全唔信任既態度<br />\n我有做好多野補救<br />\n我應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc59942e55ef32e265a3da5630fb13276a69252a","tid":1139494,"uid":14606,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T10:11:37.000Z","msg":"應該放過好女仔"},{"pid":"f17f47b0ed2e5b29c398f22180db0835c54d4dfd","tid":1139494,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dc59942e55ef32e265a3da5630fb13276a69252a","tid":1139494,"uid":14606,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T10:11:37.000Z","msg":"應該放過好女仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T10:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012b199451dc8af255c555bbea565cee054d6a0a","tid":1139494,"uid":176907,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T10:32:05.000Z","msg":"叫佢睇你依個po"},{"pid":"503b7537ef6f58013a6ccfa32a5fc44cf0a6c5b0","tid":1139494,"uid":152612,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T10:32:56.000Z","msg":"你真係水洗都唔清"},{"pid":"469763f71b6b8e8fd5549225887c225805e0b56e","tid":1139494,"uid":119421,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T10:35:30.000Z","msg":"點解係當面同前度交代有新女友<br />\n而唔係當面同現任講你而家開post嘅內容<br />\n你諗真啲你放低ex未啦"},{"pid":"daffb796314907c6430a0dfd5de28aadee54a6b1","tid":1139494,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"469763f71b6b8e8fd5549225887c225805e0b56e","tid":1139494,"uid":119421,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T10:35:30.000Z","msg":"點解係當面同前度交代有新女友<br />\n而唔係當面同現任講你而家開post嘅內容<br />\n你諗真啲你放低ex未啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T12:33:37.000Z","msg":"我有講過以上既內容比而家既佢知<br />\n同埋我真係放低哂"},{"pid":"e1c4bbd0ae3e81748b9c65cb4c5c8ebe9e8cda05","tid":1139494,"uid":197169,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:20:16.000Z","msg":"你講到放低晒 2017年又分左手<br />\n點解可以個名改都唔改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係個女仔都唔信你啦"},{"pid":"fc4fdb8e39a7fca9de1a88b1604ac0ddb7e22e1d","tid":1139494,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e1c4bbd0ae3e81748b9c65cb4c5c8ebe9e8cda05","tid":1139494,"uid":197169,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:20:16.000Z","msg":"你講到放低晒 2017年又分左手<br />\n點解可以個名改都唔改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係個女仔都唔信你啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:25:12.000Z","msg":"係既 唔信我好正常既"},{"pid":"cdb581c89d1c12fbc49ab11a96e56777e3feb273","tid":1139494,"uid":197169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fc4fdb8e39a7fca9d